item.title: CVE-2019-10795|2024-08-04T22:32:02.035Z -- snyk -- undefsafe
item.description: undefsafe before 2.0.3 is vulnerable to Prototype Pollution. The 'a' function could be tricked into adding or modifying properties of Object.prototype using a __proto__ payload.
